lexicon = 
  heat, poke, red, sit, yam, gawk, lag, tim, doop, back

Normal state
  Back - return to normal state
  Tim - change focus
  Yam - windows
    Tim - minimize
    Doop - unminimize
    Gawk - snap right
    Sit - snap left
  Poke - launch
    heat - firefox
    gawk - terminal
  Doop - type a key
    Yam - press f
    Red - press 0
    Tim - press 1
    Sit - press 2
    Lag - press enter
    Heat - open interesting links
  Red - Close current thing
  Gawk - no-op
  Heat - no-op
  Sit - no-op
  Lag - no-op
